<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Φίλων Ζήνωνι χαίρειν. εἰ ἔρρωσαι 

    <lb n="2"/>αὐτός τε καὶ οὓς θέλεις, εὖ ἂν ἔχοι· 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐρρώμην δὲ καὶ αὐτός. καλῶς ποι-

    <lb n="4"/>ήσεις ὑπὲρ ὧν Πτολεμαῖος 

    <lb n="5"/>ἀδελφὸς ἀναπέπλευκεν πρὸς 

    <lb n="ms,6"/>σέ 

    <lb n="6"/>ἐπιμελῶς διοικήσας, ἵνα τα-

    <lb n="7"/>χέως πρός με ἀναστρέφηι 

    <lb n="8"/>καὶ μὴ ἐπικωλύωμαι ἐὰν 

    <lb n="9"/>δέηι ἀναπλεῖν· συντόμως γὰρ 

    <lb n="10"/>δεῖ ἀποτρέχειν ἐντεῦθεν. 

    <lb n="11"/>ἔγραψα δέ σοι καὶ περὶ Ἑρμοκράτου 

    <lb n="12"/>πρότερον, διὰ τὸ ηἰσθῆσθαί σε σπεύ-

    <lb n="13"/>δονθ᾽ ὑπὲρ αὐτοῦ καὶ αὐτὸς φα-

    <lb n="14"/>νερὸν αὐτῶι <choice><corr>πεποιηκέναι</corr><sic>πεποηκε<add place="supralinear">ναι</add></sic></choice>, καὶ σφό-

    <lb n="15"/>δρ᾽ οἴομαι ἡμερῶν ὀλίγων ἔξω 

    <lb n="16"/>αὐτὸν ἔσεσθαι. <choice><corr>ἐνωχλήθησαν</corr><sic>ηνωχληθησαν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="17"/>δ᾽ ὑπὲρ αὐτοῦ καὶ πλείους, 

    <lb n="18"/>ἐπετέλεσεν δὲ μάλιστα Κα-

    <lb n="19"/>φισοφῶν ὁ Φιλίππου τοῦ ἰατροῦ υἱός. 

    <lb n="20"/>καὶ τὴν ἀνάκρισιν τὴν ὑπὲρ 

    <lb n="21"/>αὐτοῦ γεγραμμένην, ἣ καὶ 

    <lb n="22"/>ἐπέλυεν αὐτὸν πάντων τῶν 

    <lb n="23"/>ἐπικληθέντων, εἶχεν ἤδη Δωσί-

    <lb n="24"/>θεος ὁ ὑπομνηματογράφος, ἵνα 

    <lb n="25"/>ὁ βασιλεὺς ἐπαναγνῶι πρὸ τοῦ 

    <lb n="26"/>ἀφεθῆναι <add place="supralinear">αὐτόν</add>, παρὰ τὸ ἔθος εἶναι οὕ-

    <lb n="27"/><add place="supralinear">τως γίνεσθαι</add>. τὰ δ᾽ ἄλλα συντόμως προσδέ-

    <lb n="28"/>χου καὶ αὐτοὺς ἡμᾶς· καὶ τῶν 

    <lb n="29"/>ἐν οἴκωι δέ, κἂν αὐτὸς θλίβηι 

    <lb n="30"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δ</unclear>ιατηρήσ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ας</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἐ</unclear>μο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῦ</unclear> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τὸ</unclear>ν τόπ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>ν τ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="31"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/> 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="31"/>Ζήνωνι. 

    <lb n="31"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied>ἰς Φιλα-

    <lb n="32"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δ</supplied>έλφειαν. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.1955" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1955" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" precision="low" notBefore="-0240-02" notAfter="-0240-03">ca. Febr. - März 240 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1955" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Mich.</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">55</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">1955</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0163</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">55</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0163;1;55" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1955" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.1955" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">C.Pap.Jud. I 127a</bibl></div><div n="meta.1955" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de" default="NO"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">TUAT, N.F. 3 (2006), VIII 3.1.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="fr" default="NO"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Orrieux, Les papyrus de Zenon (1983), S. 69</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.1955" type="history" subtype="loca